import React from "react"; import Selfie from '../bus-selfie.jpg'; const AboutMe = () => { return (

about me

Hi, I am Sean Williams, a web developer from Dublin, Ireland. I created this website as an interactive way to get to know me and showcase some development skills. I have been programming for over 10 years, orignally starting out with a 300 page book that thought you how to make websites and I have been developing ever since. Over this time I have gathered experiance in multiple different programming languages such Java, Python, Angular, Javascript, C++, Haskell and many more. I studied Enterprise Computing at Dublin City Univercity graduating in 2019 with Honours Bachelor's Degree and I am in the process of obtaining my Masters from Technological University Dublin in Advanced Software Development. I joined AIG after college as part of a rotation program that allowed me to get experiance in different areas of software development so that I can now work as a full stack developer. Other then all that, some of my hobbies include teaching, basketball, esports If I had to describe my self, I think the best way to put it is that I am big nerd who loves American sports that wants to create interesting and usefull web applcations. Im always open to anybody who ever wants to talk job oppurtunites, emerging technologies or NBA results, please dont be shy and reach out to me.

) } export default AboutMe
